details.name: Earth Splitter
details.description: Sends forth a jagged crack in front of Elder Titan. After 3 seconds, the crack implodes, slowing movement while dealing damage to each enemy based on their maximum life. Half of the damage dealt is Magical damage, while the other half is Physical damage. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.
details.upgrade_description: Increases slow duration, and units pulled in by Earth Splitter are also disarmed.
